comments: People most likely will not see this. This video is rather old at this point. Using this video and changing my diet slightly. I lost 120 lbs over this past year. I will go on to upgrade myself to the longer workouts on Hasfit's channel. I love what you two have done for my life. I hope some person out there can read this commet and know that it is possible!
i actually finished a weights workout? me with my noodle arms???? holy heck ive never been more proud of myself. thank you for this video!

I've been doing this video in my little apartment during covid lockdown and it's one of my favorites I've come across so far. I'm at the tail end of chemotherapy and trying to build my muscle back up. It's challenging but not to the points of being unable to complete it. Thank you for making this!
My arms are burning and I love it.  I have lost 39 pounds over the last three months with diet and exercise.   This is a wonderful video... Who would give it a thumbs down???  Stay motivated......
This is by far the most realistic beginner strength training video I’ve ever seen. Finished it and feeling the burn.
